&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 4–5 years in the life sciences. A technical background in AI/ML based antibody engineering and/or antibody characterization is preferred. Familiarity with Salesforce and Jira is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
