&lt;p&gt;The Staff Product Manager will be responsible for all aspects of product management&amp;nbsp;for Twist Bioscience Protein Solutions product portfolio. This includes assessing and&amp;nbsp;prioritizing customer and market requirements, working in collaboration with strategic&amp;nbsp;collaborators, product development, production, and commercial team to deliver&amp;nbsp;disruptive products as it relates to high throughput protein/antibody production and&amp;nbsp;characterization.&lt;/p&gt;
