&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In collaboration with the commercial team, the Protein Solutions product manager will own and be responsible for growing the Protein Solutions high throughput product and services portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with customers and strategic partners to gather input to develop disruptive new products and services&lt;/li&gt;
