&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated track record of managing multiple high-profile collaborations that&amp;nbsp;deliver successful products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5-8 years of relevant work experience in the life sciences or related field, with &amp;gt;5&amp;nbsp;years in product management/marketing positions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree in molecular biology, protein science or associated scientific field. A&amp;nbsp;Ph.D., MBA or other advanced degree desirable.&lt;/li&gt;
