&lt;li&gt;Good verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to lift 40 lbs. on a regula

&lt;p&gt;Twist Bioscience is seeking a visionary and highly accomplished leader to lead our global marketing organization, define our brand narrative, and drive sustainable, significant growth across all business units. The Senior Director/ VP, Global Marketing will report to the SVP of Product and Marketing and hold accountability for setting the global marketing vision, strategy, and execution across markets and regions. This leader will be responsible for translating business objectives into high-impact marketing strategies, overseeing brand, product positioning, integrated global campaigns, growth marketing, digital channels, and executive-level customer engagement.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
